---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
---

<Base
  title="About"
  description="Learn about Eric Davidson-Sawyer, a web developer based in South Berwick, ME, helping local businesses build their online presence."
>
  <section class="page-header">
    <div class="container">
      <h1>About</h1>
      <p>A little bit about me and how I work.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="about-content">
        <div class="about-text">
          <h2>Hi, I'm Eric</h2>

          <p>
            Software engineer based in South Berwick, Maine. After years building
            software for companies large and small, I started helping local businesses
            get online.
          </p>

          <p>
            Too many local businesses have outdated websites, no website, or are
            overpaying for basic services. I offer straightforward, fairly-priced
            web development that actually fits small business needs.
          </p>

          <h3>My Approach</h3>

          <p>Simple. You don't need a complicated website. You need one that:</p>

          <ul>
            <li>Looks professional</li>
            <li>Loads fast</li>
            <li>Works on phones</li>
            <li>Shows up on Google</li>
            <li>Makes it easy to contact you</li>
          </ul>

          <p>That's what I build. No fluff. No jargon. No surprise fees.</p>

          <h3>Why Local?</h3>

          <p>
            I shop at your stores and eat at your restaurants. When you succeed,
            our whole community benefits.
          </p>

          <p>
            Plus, being local means I'm actually available. Coffee meetings, not
            just Zoom calls.
          </p>
        </div>

        <aside class="about-sidebar">
          <div class="sidebar-box">
            <h3>Technical Background</h3>
            <ul>
              <li>10+ years software engineering</li>
              <li>Full-stack development</li>
              <li>Modern web technologies</li>
              <li>Performance optimization</li>
              <li>SEO best practices</li>
            </ul>
          </div>

          <div class="sidebar-box">
            <h3>Based In</h3>
            <p>South Berwick, ME</p>
            <p class="text-light">Serving the Seacoast region of Maine and New Hampshire</p>
          </div>
        </aside>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section section-alt">
    <div class="container text-center">
      <h2>Let's Talk</h2>
      <p class="text-light">
        Have a project in mind? Let's see if we're a good fit.
      </p>
      <a href="/contact" class="btn mt-2">Get in Touch</a>
    </div>
  </section>
</Base>

<style>
  .page-header {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f0f9ff 0%, #e0f2fe 100%);
    padding: 4rem 0;
  }

  .page-header h1 {
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }

  .page-header p {
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    color: var(--color-text-light);
    margin: 0;
  }

  .about-content {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 300px;
    gap: 3rem;
    align-items: start;
  }

  .about-text h2 {
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }

  .about-text h3 {
    margin-top: 2rem;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .about-text p {
    color: var(--color-text-light);
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .about-text ul {
    padding-left: 1.5rem;
    color: var(--color-text-light);
  }

  .about-text li {
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }

  .about-sidebar {
    position: sticky;
    top: calc(var(--header-height) + 2rem);
  }

  .sidebar-box {
    background: var(--color-bg-alt);
    padding: 1.5rem;
    border-radius: 0.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }

  .sidebar-box h3 {
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    font-size: 1rem;
  }

  .sidebar-box ul {
    list-style: none;
    padding: 0;
    margin: 0;
  }

  .sidebar-box li {
    padding: 0.25rem 0;
    color: var(--color-text-light);
  }

  .sidebar-box p {
    margin: 0.25rem 0;
  }

  @media (max-width: 900px) {
    .about-content {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }

    .about-sidebar {
      position: static;
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(200px, 1fr));
      gap: 1rem;
    }

    .sidebar-box {
      margin-bottom: 0;
    }
  }
</style>
